}}

'''蘋果公司'''（{{lang-en|Apple Inc.}}），原稱'''蘋果電脑公司'''（{{lang-en|Apple Computer, Inc.}}），是总部位于[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亞州|加州]][[庫比蒂諾_(加利福尼亞州)|庫比蒂諾]]的[[跨國公司|跨國]][[科技公司|科技公司]]，与[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊]]、[[Google|谷歌]]、[[微软|微软]]、[[Meta_Platforms|Meta]]合稱為五大[[科技巨擘|科技巨擘]]。現時的業務包括设计、开发、手机通信和销售[[消费电子|消费电子]]、[[计算机软件|计算机软件]]、在线服务和个人计算机。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ranking The Big Four Tech Stocks: Google Is No. 1, Apple Comes In Last|url=http://www.barrons.com/articles/ranking-the-big-four-internet-stocks-google-is-no-1-apple-comes-in-last-1503412102|last=Rivas|first=Teresa|language=|dead-url=no|website=www.barrons.com|access-date=2018-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228082808/https://www.barrons.com/articles/ranking-the-big-four-internet-stocks-google-is-no-1-apple-comes-in-last-1503412102|archive-date=2018-12-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Big Four of Technology|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2017-10-31/the-big-four-of-technology|date=2017-10-31|last=Ritholtz|first=Barry|dead-url=no|website=Bloomberg L.P.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626024146/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2017-10-31/the-big-four-of-technology|archive-date=2019-06-26|access-date=2018-12-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is GAFA (the Big Four)? - Definition from WhatIs.com|url=https://whatis.techtarget.com/definition/GAFA|language=|website=WhatIs.com|access-date=2020-03-05|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001123/https://whatis.techtarget.com/definition/GAFA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1976年4月，[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]、[[斯蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克|斯蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克]]和[[罗纳德·韦恩|罗纳德·韦恩]]创立了苹果公司，目的是为了开发和销售沃兹尼亚克[[Apple_I|Apple I]]个人电脑，但韦恩12天后就放弃了自己的股份。1977年1月，正式确定公司名称为苹果电脑公司（Apple Computer, Inc.），包括[[Apple_II|Apple II]]在内的电脑销量迅速增长。几年之内，乔布斯和沃兹尼亚克就雇佣了一批电脑设计师，并拥有了一条生产线。1980年，苹果公司[[首次公开募股|上市]]，迅速获得了财务上的成功。在接下来的几年里，苹果公司推出了具有[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]的新电脑，如1984年推出的{{tsl|en|Macintosh 128K||}}，同时苹果公司的产品营销广告得到广泛好评。然而，其产品的高价格和有限的应用程序引发了许多问题，其高管之间的权力斗争不断。1985年，沃兹尼亚克离开了苹果公司，继续担任名誉雇员<ref name="wozemployee">{{Cite news|url=http://woz.org/letters/never-left-apple/|title=I Never Left Apple|date=2018-01-03|work=Officially Woz|access-date=2018-10-02|language=|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327162321/http://woz.org/letters/never-left-apple/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而乔布斯和其他人则辞职成立了[[NeXT|NeXT]]公司<ref name="rice19850415">{{Cite news |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=zC4EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA35 |title= Unrecognized Apple II Employees Exit |work= {{tsl|en|InfoWorld||InfoWorld}} |date= 1985-04-15 |last= Rice |first= Valerie |page= 35 |accessdate= 2020-10-29 |archive-date= 2021-05-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001050/https://books.google.com/books?id=zC4EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA35 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。1996年，蘋果收購NeXT公司，賈伯斯於隔年重返蘋果，率領蘋果成為科技巨擘。

该公司最著名的[[计算机硬件|硬件]]产品有[[iPhone|iPhone]]智能手机、[[iPad|iPad]]平板电脑、[[麥金塔|Mac]]个人电脑、[[iPod|iPod]]音乐播放器、[[Apple_Watch|Apple Watch]]智能手表、[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]媒体播放器 、[[AirPods|AirPods]]无线耳机和[[HomePod|HomePod]]智能音箱、遊戲機 Pippin atmark ；[[软件|软件]]有[[macOS|macOS]]、[[iOS|iOS]]、[[iPadOS|iPadOS]]、[[watchOS|watchOS]]和[[tvOS|tvOS]]五大[[操作系统|操作系统]]、[[iTunes|iTunes]]播放器、[[Safari|Safari]]网页浏览器 、[[Shazam_(服務)|Shazam]]音乐识别，还有[[iLife|iLife]]和[[iWork|iWork]]创意和生产力套件，以及[[Final_Cut_Pro|Final Cut Pro]]、[[Logic_Pro|Logic Pro]]和[[Xcode|Xcode]]等专业软件；在线服务有[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]、[[App_Store_(iOS/iPadOS)|iOS App Store]]、[[Mac_App_Store|Mac App Store]]、[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]、[[Apple_TV+|Apple TV+]]、[[iMessage|iMessage]]和[[iCloud|iCloud]]。苹果公司还有其他一系列服务包括[[Apple_Store|Apple Store]]、[[Genius_Bar|Genius Bar]]、[[AppleCare|AppleCare]]、[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]、[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay Cash]]和[[Apple_Card|Apple Card]]等。

2018[[財政年度|财年]]，苹果公司全球总收入总计2,650亿美元。按收入计算，苹果是[[最大的信息技术公司列表|全球最大的科技公司]]，也是[[按市值排列的上市公司列表|全球市值最高的公司]]之一。它也是仅次于[[三星集团|三星]]的世界第二大手机制造商。2018年8月，苹果成为第一家市值超过1万亿美元的美国上市公司，<ref name="1t-CNBC">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/02/apple-hits-1-trillion-in-market-value.html|title=Apple just hit a $1 trillion market cap|last=Salinas|first=Sara|date=2018-08-02|publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|access-date=2018-08-02|archive-date=2020-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528131244/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/02/apple-hits-1-trillion-in-market-value.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="1t-Guardian">{{Cite web |first=Rob |last=Davies |title=Apple becomes world's first trillion dollar company |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/aug/02/apple-becomes-worlds-first-trillion-dollar-company |website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2018-08-02 |access-date=2018-08-02 |archive-date=2020-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428201743/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/aug/02/apple-becomes-worlds-first-trillion-dollar-company |dead-url=no }}</ref>两年后的2020年8月，它成为了第一家市值达到2万亿美元的美国公司，<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-53840471|title=Apple first US company to be valued at $2tn|work=BBC News|date=2020-08-19|accessdate=2020-08-19|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117155636/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-53840471|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Nicas|first1=Jack|title=Apple Reaches $2 Trillion, Punctuating Big Tech's Grip|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/19/technology/apple-2-trillion.html|accessdate=2020-08-21|work=The New York Times|date=2020-08-19|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001115/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/19/technology/apple-2-trillion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2022年1月，它成為了第一家市值達到3兆美元的公司。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2022-01-03|title=Apple becomes first US company to reach $3tn valuation|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2022/jan/03/apple-becomes-first-us-company-to-reach-3tn-valuation|access-date=2022-01-03|website=the Guardian|language=en}}</ref> {{As of|2020|lc=y}}，苹果公司拥有13.7万名全职员工，<ref name="Apple-Inc-Nov-2017-10-K">{{Cite web|title=Apple Inc, Form 10-K, Annual Report, Filing Date January 28, 2020|url=https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0000320193/1a919118-a594-44f3-92f0-4ecca47b1a7d.pdf|publisher=secdatabase.com|access-date=2020-01-28|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224204619/https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0000320193/1a919118-a594-44f3-92f0-4ecca47b1a7d.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>在25个国家拥有510家[[Apple_Store|零售店]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Retail Store – Store List|url=https://www.apple.com/retail/storelist/|publisher=Apple|language=|access-date=2020-06-03|archive-date=2011-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110215221937/http://www.apple.com/retail/storelist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{As of|2020|1}}，全球约有15亿件苹果产品在被活跃使用中。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2020/01/28/apple-1-5-billion-active-devices-worldwide/|title=Apple Now Has 1.5 Billion Active Devices Worldwide|access-date=2020-01-28|language=|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001124/https://www.macrumors.com/2020/01/28/apple-1-5-billion-active-devices-worldwide/|dead-url=no}}</ref>苹果公司还拥有很高的[[品牌忠誠度|品牌忠誠度]]，并被评为世界最具价值品牌。但是，苹果公司在其产业链中的劳工制度、环境和商业实践中至今仍然飽受批评<ref>{{Cite web|title=苹果背后的生与死|url=https://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/ch/8826-Dying-for-an-iPhone-the-lives-of-Chinese-workers|language=|dead-url=yes|website=www.chinadialogue.net|access-date=2018-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180501092926/https://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/ch/8826-Dying-for-an-iPhone-the-lives-of-Chinese-workers|archive-date=2018-05-01}}</ref>。

