=== HomePod ===
{{Main|HomePod}}
[[File:An_Apple_HomePod_speaker_.png|thumb]]]]
2017年6月5日，苹果发布了首款智能音箱[[HomePod|HomePod]]，于2018年2月9日开始发售。HomePod的底座有7个高音[[扬声器|扬声器]]，顶部有一个4英寸的低音扬声器，以及6个用于语音控制和声音优化的[[麦克风|麦克风]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/2/12/17003296/homepod-repair-ifixit-teardown|title=This iFixit teardown shows the HomePod is built like a tank|work=The Verge|access-date=2018-02-14|archive-date=2018-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212212259/https://www.theverge.com/2018/2/12/17003296/homepod-repair-ifixit-teardown|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/7/31/16067710/apple-leaked-homepod-firmware-os-third-party-apps|title=HomePod firmware reveals more secrets of Apple's smart speaker|last=Ong|first=Thuy|date=2017-07-31|website=The Verge|access-date=2017-09-03|archive-date=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904063324/https://www.theverge.com/2017/7/31/16067710/apple-leaked-homepod-firmware-os-third-party-apps|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wired-review">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/review/review-apple-homepod/|title=HomePod Review: Only Apple Devotees Need Apply|website=Wired.com|language=|access-date=2018-02-14|archive-date=2018-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215083738/https://www.wired.com/review/review-apple-homepod/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年10月14日，苹果发布了[[HomePod_mini|HomePod mini]]。

=== 軟體 ===
{{Main|macOS|iOS|iPadOS|watchOS|tvOS}}
[[File:WWDC_2011_Moscone_West_Exterior.jpg|缩略图]]，向软件开发者展示其新的软件和技术。]]

苹果为自己的产品开发了自己的[[操作系统|操作系统]]，包括用于Mac的[[macOS|macOS]]，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple to release macOS Sierra on September 20th|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/7/12758218/apple-mac-os-sierra-update-release-date-announced|date=2016-09-07|last=Statt|first=Nick|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001724/https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/7/12758218/apple-mac-os-sierra-update-release-date-announced|dead-url=no}}</ref>用于[[iPhone|iPhone]]和[[iPod_Touch|iPod Touch]]的[[iOS|iOS]]，用于[[iPad|iPad]]的[[iPadOS|iPadOS]]，<ref>{{Cite web|title=iOS 10 will be available on September 13th|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/7/12739682/apple-ios-10-update-release-date-features-announced|date=2016-09-07|last=Warren|first=Tom|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001643/https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/7/12739682/apple-ios-10-update-release-date-features-announced|dead-url=no}}</ref>用于[[Apple_Watch|Apple Watch]]的[[watchOS|watchOS]]，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple overhauls watchOS with new UI and faster app launching|url=https://techcrunch.com/2016/06/13/apple-overhauls-watchos-with-new-ui-and-faster-app-launching/|date=2016-06-13|last=Tepper|first=Fitz|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514003156/https://techcrunch.com/2016/06/13/apple-overhauls-watchos-with-new-ui-and-faster-app-launching/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及用于[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]的[[tvOS|tvOS]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple just released tvOS 10 and here's what's new|url=https://techcrunch.com/2016/09/13/apple-just-released-tvos-10-and-heres-whats-new/|date=2016-09-13|last=Dillet|first=Romain|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001701/https://techcrunch.com/2016/09/13/apple-just-released-tvos-10-and-heres-whats-new/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

针对iOS、iPadOS和macOS，苹果开发了iWork办公套件，包括用于写作的[[Pages|Pages]]、用于电子表格的[[Numbers|Numbers]]和用于演示的[[Keynote|Keynote]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=iWork|url=https://www.apple.com/iwork/|website=Apple Inc.|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2007-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070814024014/http://www.apple.com/iwork/|dead-url=no}}</ref>对于macOS，苹果还开发了[[iMovie|iMovie]]和[[Final_Cut_Pro|Final Cut Pro]]用于视频编辑，<ref>{{Cite web|title=iMovie and Final Cut Pro for Mac Get Bug Fixes in New Updates|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2017/04/13/imovie-for-mac-bug-fix-update/|date=2017-04-13|last=Clover|first=Juli|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514001720/https://www.macrumors.com/2017/04/13/imovie-for-mac-bug-fix-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[GarageBand|GarageBand]]和[[Logic_Pro|Logic Pro]]用于音乐创作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple releases huge updates for music apps GarageBand and Logic Pro X|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/apple-music-garageband-logic-pro-x-macbook-pro-touch-bar-update-103-a7534906.html|date=2017-01-19|last=Griffin|first=Andrew|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728022803/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/apple-music-garageband-logic-pro-x-macbook-pro-touch-bar-update-103-a7534906.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

苹果还通过[[iCloud|iCloud]]提供在线服务，iCloud为大量用户提供云存储和同步，包括文档、照片、音乐、设备备份和应用程序数据，<ref>{{Cite web|title=iCloud|url=https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/icloud/|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303025823/https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/icloud/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及音乐和视频流服务[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Music|url=https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/apple-music/|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|access-date=2017-06-09|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417090022/https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/apple-music/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

